{"tid":128611,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪有野搞我？","createTime":"2017-02-21T03:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T16:50:01.000Z","uid":31801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ccf82c56bf32fc9b211498a4152d8f229e5a7ce","tid":128611,"uid":31801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"前晚訓覺夢到個五官好模糊既人，唔記得係白光定綠光 <br />\n雖然合埋左眼，但感覺係佢直情係你面前四目交投咁，好真實 <br />\n以為普通發惡夢，點知琴晚訓到迷迷糊糊聽到耳邊有聲，好似有人講野咁，搞到醒左成晚訓唔返<br />\n雖然唔係好驚依d野，但晚晚咁搞法真係無覺好訓<br />\n唔知究竟係我幻覺定點，想問點先知係咪真係有野?"},{"pid":"015ab2c217af49f16f9636de2844d55556aea907","tid":128611,"uid":75502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"323e713e6221faa387c72a100a22c5ce8a0bdea1","tid":128611,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:43:06.000Z","msg":"等我幫你趕走佢"},{"pid":"f3eb34cbfbe5dddffaa2d8b8905517a860137b85","tid":128611,"uid":75502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b76d5232f3172d09188c6054084ddae145dea409","tid":128611,"uid":74830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:32:17.000Z","msg":"大聲講再嘈姦咗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517ec82a48db16927a483810f5cbe0652c0959be","tid":128611,"uid":75502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac0f30773b6582916054c9aa4a0bfb59ecf70dfd","tid":128611,"uid":76744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"細個訓到十二點到又係見過白光綠光人  連續左幾晚  仲要嘔埋 你似中野 今晚再睇睇點"},{"pid":"8a65b9cb7cad09ebf432f8c9312d52de81ee8236","tid":128611,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"去求道平安符吧"},{"pid":"4f4385efb869a9e09d2934fdacde7f10e7fa8b02","tid":128611,"uid":13948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:50:01.